{"tid":1820752,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"仝香港人, 要一齊親自向陳巧文道歉","createTime":"2020-01-11T16:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T06:31:01.000Z","uid":76310,"like":628,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"8d28759b3f4c4678fbf1e214b95b0959858b19ee","tid":1820752,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:55:35.000Z","msg":"仝香港人, 要一齊親自向陳巧文道歉<br />\n當日佢走得太前, 要求西藏民族自決, 根本沒有錯<br />\n但大量既人攻擊她, 和她的親人和朋友<br />\n加上中共港共攪佢<br />\n佢承受了很多<br />\n<br />\n你地找個時間, 一齊誠心的向她道歉, 和她說對不起, 好嗎<br />\n(利申先, 由以前到而家, 我都對中共無好感, 理由好簡單, 64單野永遠記住, 就係咁簡單, <br />\n所以自問唔會道歉, 因為當日我無攻擊過她, 也讚同呢樣主張)"},{"pid":"c4704cd4a96eee27b7e39f827cc9e1d18ac8b423","tid":1820752,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c7f90d033165c01cabaf2572640ced37bb19cf","tid":1820752,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:57:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c271c53d94d41959d2b91eaf6d9da89546ab7f96","tid":1820752,"uid":343361,"like":43,"dislike":14,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">贏就係最好嘅道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"90229ef0b4062689e91cfe58ccdec699b78504ee","tid":1820752,"uid":24345,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"Twitter 做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36a6be02a387466db963e5f5183e57107a8e121","tid":1820752,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d99601a98185f745938d0e401c21081a610260a","tid":1820752,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:00:33.000Z","msg":"要一齊親自誠心向陳巧文